# If your joystick is listed in here, you don't have to try to find
# the correct numbers for your axes/buttons.
#
# If you want to contribute the settings for your joystick to this
# list, please mail them to <mitch@uni.de>. You can use this template:
# 

   example entry for analog device
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

added by Your Name <your@email>

Action            | Event            | Values ([a]nalog / [d]igital)
------------------+------------------+---------------------------------------
Left              | Axis 1 low       | [a] 0 to -32767

