  T A B L E   O F   C O N T E N T S  for joyd v0.2.1
  =================================

  (no changes since 0.2.0)

    - Gravis GamePad Pro (USB)
    - Microsoft Sidewinder Force Feedback Pro
    - Super Nintendo Joypad


