#############################################################################


   Gravis GamePad Pro (USB)
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

added by Stephane Louise <luigi@fleming.u-psud.fr>

        Driver is USB backport from 2.3.42 to 2.2.14
        (shouldn't be different in 2.4 final)

Action            | Event            | Values ([a]nalog / [d]igital)
------------------+------------------+---------------------------------------
Left              | Axis 1 low       | [d] -32767
Right             | Axis 1 high      | [d]  32767
Up                | Axis 2 low       | [d] -32767
Down              | Axis 2 high      | [d]  32767
Button "Red(Left)"| Button 1         |
Button "Yellow(B)"| Button 2         |
Button "Green(R)" | Button 3         |
Button "Blue(Top)"| Button 4         |
Button "L1"       | Button 5         |
Button "R1"       | Button 6         |
Button "L2"       | Button 7         |
Button "R2"       | Button 8         |
Button "Select"   | Button 9         |
Button "Start"    | Button 10        |


#############################################################################


   Microsoft Sidewinder Force Feedback Pro
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

added by Derrick Pallas <omegakon@bigfoot.com>

This description is quite long and won't fit into the template.
Please read the file CONFIG.SidewinderFFP


#############################################################################


   Super Nintendo Joypad
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

added by Christian Garbs <mitch@uni.de>

(on parallel port, see /usr/src/linux/Documentation/joystick-parport.txt)

Action            | Event            | Values ([a]nalog / [d]igital)
------------------+------------------+---------------------------------------
Left              | Axis 1 low       | [d] -32767
Right             | Axis 1 high      | [d]  32767
Up                | Axis 2 low       | [d] -32767
Down              | Axis 2 high      | [d]  32767
Button "A"        | Button 1         |
Button "B"        | Button 2         |
Button "X"        | Button 3         |
Button "Y"        | Button 4         |
Button "L"        | Button 5         |
Button "R"        | Button 6         |
Button "Select"   | Button 7         |
Button "Start"    | Button 8         |


